Author: securethebag
Title: [ANN] Centra Tech | Multi-Blockchain Worldwide Debit Card & Insured Wallet
Body: Open Letter To Community:  I want to thank every single one of our members, contributors, supporters for the unconditional love & support the last 36 hours. I can personally say the amount of messages showing full support to the team and myself in regards to our project have been heart warming and humbling. We do everything for you guys, we are excited just as much as the next person when we see a Centra Card prepared to be shipped.  We all stuck together through an onslaught attack from a very well planned out attacker. We triumphed over this hurdle and we will officially continue our ICO as 15.9M tokens are still left for sale. There will be many exciting updates throughout the next few days as time progresses.  We have been officially added as a member of the Ethereum Alliance before our competitors, our second celebrity endorser next to Floyd Mayweather JR is DJ Khaled, our Centra Wallet Beta is back on track to be complete for the end of the month, and a lot more that I will discuss in a Blog post.  Once again, thank you, sincerely, to everyone for sticking through this with us, from day one till day present, the Centra Team will ensure that we create the best Commerce to Crypto products in the market!  @everyone stay safe, be strong, and continue to push forward!  Thank you, Sam    I'm proud to be a day 1 supporter of Centra. The team and community are only getting stronger each and every day! Excited to see where we are in a year from now #Centratothemoon #Centrafam

Error encountered during contract execution [Bad instruction]'  I'm minded not to try again because I'm waisting funds, unless maybe someone could advise me why both my TXs failed please?
